import React from "react"; import '../styles/steps_for_voting.css' const Setup_for_voting = () => { return (

Register to vote for your favorite candidate

To register and vote. follow the steps to create and vote for your favorite candidate

Step1: Enter your email

Enter your email to receive the otp we will send to you

Step2: Fill up the form with your detail

This process is to create an account you will use to login

Step3: Verify it is you

Input your email and phone number/code that you used to create your guest account

Step4: Start voting

You can start voting when you are done, click on submit

) } export default Setup_for_voting
